eation of a process and the source.","false_positives":"","false_negatives":"","documentable":"false","security_override_guidance":"","potential_impacts":"","third_party_tools":"","ia_controls":"","responsibility":"","mitigations":"","mitigation_control":"","legacy_ids":[],"ccis":["CCI-000172"],"reference_identifier":"8372","uuid":"ded63b4f-5ad3-429e-8d50-23828af05bd9","stig_uuid":"c72758fa-0fec-48d0-b90f-cf02bbeace21","status":"not_applicable","overrides":{},"comments":"Not applicable - capability not installed/enabled on this asset.","finding_details":"Evaluate-STIG 1.2604.2 (Scan-Windows7_Checks) marked this Not_Applicable on 07/23/2026\r\nResultHash: E7314BA9A613E5226D29C5C672FA709174323E25\r\n~~~~~\r\nThe feature/role addressed by 'The system will be configured to audit \"Detailed Tracking -> Process Creation\" successes.' is not present or not in use on this the Windows 7 workstation."},{"group_id_src":"V-26540","group_tree":[{"id":"V-26540","title":"Audit - Logoff - Success","description":"<GroupDescription></GroupDescription>"}],"group_id":"V-26540","severity":"medium","group_title":"Audit - Logoff - Success","rule_id_src":"SV-35984r1_rule","rule_id":"SV-35984","rule_version":"WINAU-000505","rule_title":"The system will be configured to audit \"Logon/Logoff -> Logoff\" successes.","fix_text":"Detailed auditing subcategories are configured in Security Settings -> Advanced Audit Policy Configuration.   The summary level settings under Security Settings -> Local Policies -> Audit Policy will not be enforced (see V-14230).\n\nConfigure the policy value for Computer Configuration -> Windows Settings -> Security Settings -> Advanced Audit Policy Configuration -> System Audit Policies -> Logon/Logoff -> \"Audit Logoff\" with \u201cSuccess\u201d selected.","weight":"10.0","check_content":"Security Option \u201cAudit: Force audit policy subcategory settings (Windows Vista or later) to override audit policy category settings\u201d must be set to \u201cEnabled\u201d (V